---
title: Thai Coconut Beef & Udon Noodles with Broccoli & Mint
description: The star of this sumptuous noodle number is our Thai red curry paste, which has a mild flavour the whole family will love.  A perfect balance of easy and tasty, we reckon you’ll be losing the Thai takeaway’s number once you've tried it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-coconut-beef-lime-noodles-a90af895.jpg
